排」明顯有落差。試述某甲可否主張公平交易法第21 條不實廣告，並要
求取消契約。（25 分）
33140', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:16+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "318589c1b27e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "328", "s": "1017", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公平交易法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "公平交易管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
